comments: Harris (BKN) briefly places an arm around Allen (CLE) and immediately slides it off.
Claxton (BKN) makes clean contact with the ball and any contact with LeVert's (CLE) hand on the ball is incidental during his driving shot attempt.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Dinwiddie's (BKN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Dinwiddie (BKN) slightly extends an arm towards LeVert (BKN) during the pick but the contact is marginal.
Bridges (BKN) is in a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact initiated by Mitchell (CLE) during his driving shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) places an arm against Mitchell's (CLE) arm but the contact does not affect Mitchell's SQBR as he releases from the contact.
Finney-Smith (BKN) remains in bounds with the ball in his possession.
Dinwiddie (BKN) initiates contact to Mitchell's (CLE) left leg that affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs before Mitchell's gather and is correctly deemed a non-shooting foul.
Mitchell (CLE) crosses the plane of the free throw line before it makes contact with the rim.
Harris (BKN) reaches for the rebound and marginal arm contact occurs with Mitchell (CLE) as he attempts the putback.

Bridges (BKN) trips over Harris's (BKN) foot and causes him to fall to the floor.  Upon returning to the floor from his layup attempt, Mitchell (CLE) and Bridges make incidental foot contact with each other.
LeVert (CLE) and Bridges (BKN) engage and disengage with one another and the contact is marginal.
LeVert (CLE) legally contests Bridges's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
